# Filament v5 Conventions

Panel: `admin` at `/admin` — configured only in `AdminPanelProvider` (no `config/filament.php`).

## Resource layout (required)

```
app/Filament/Resources/{Plural}/
  {Singular}Resource.php
  Schemas/{Singular}Form.php      # Form::configure(Schema $schema)
  Tables/{Plural}Table.php        # Table::configure(Table $table)
  Pages/List|Create|Edit{...}.php
```

Use Filament `Schema` for forms (v5), not legacy Form API. Prefer native Form/Table builders over custom Blade.

## Navigation

- Groups: **Finances** (Invoices, Budgets), **Settings** (Labels, WhatsApp Connection, Backups)
- Theme: amber/zinc accents + Slate dark surfaces (see `docs/ui-dark-theme.md`), Outfit font, SPA mode, collapsible sidebar, database notifications
- Breadcrumbs: disabled panel-wide via `->breadcrumbs(false)` in `AdminPanelProvider` — do not re-enable per resource
- Custom pages: `Dashboard`, `ReceiptUploadPage`, `Auth/EditProfile`, `WhatsAppConnectionPage`

## Widgets

Dashboard widgets live in `app/Filament/Widgets/`. Month filtering uses `InteractsWithDashboardMonth` + `DashboardMonthAnalytics` / `DashboardMonthPeriod`.

## Content draft recovery

Create/Edit resource pages use `App\Filament\Concerns\RecoversContentDraft` (Invoices, Labels, Budgets). See `docs/content-draft-recovery.md` when adding a new Create/Edit page: trait + `contentDraftKey()` + register the page in `AdminPanelProvider` `PAGE_END` poller scopes.

## Prefer

- `relationship()` for related selects
- Notifications on user-facing actions
- Soft-delete aware queries (`withoutGlobalScopes` on record binding when needed)
- Icon-only row actions (View/Edit/Delete): set globally in `AppServiceProvider` via `Table::configureUsing` → `modifyUngroupedRecordActionsUsing(fn (Action $action) => $action->iconButton()->tooltip(fn (Action $action) => $action->getLabel()))` — do not re-add visible labels per table
- Filter + Column Manager triggers: Tippy tooltips globally via `filtersTriggerAction` / `columnManagerTriggerAction` in the same `Table::configureUsing` block
- List-page “New …” CTAs: plus icon set globally via `CreateAction::configureUsing` → `->icon(Heroicon::Plus)` — new List pages only need `CreateAction::make()`; do not omit/override unless intentional
- `created_at` (and similar upload timestamps) use `->since()->dateTimeTooltip()` — relative time in the cell, full date/time on hover (same as Receipt Upload “Uploaded At”)
- Icon CTA tooltips: Filament Tippy only (`->tooltip()` / `x-tooltip`) — never browser `title=` for user-facing CTAs; high-z custom modals need Tippy `zIndex: 100000` — see `docs/ui-tooltips.md`

## View records (required)

Always use slide-over view — never add a dedicated `ViewRecord` / `View{Model}` page.

- Resource tables: `ViewAction::make()->slideOver()` in `recordActions` (before Edit/Delete)
- Notification / deep-link “View” CTAs: open the resource list with Filament table-action query params so the same slide-over mounts:

```php
Resource::getUrl('index', [
    'tableAction' => 'view',
    'tableActionRecord' => $record->getRouteKey(),
]);
```

## Avoid

- Custom Blade unless native components cannot do the job
- Putting business logic (Ollama, Drive sync, alerts) inside Resource classes — call Services/Jobs
- Dedicated View pages (`ViewRecord`, `make:filament-page --type=ViewRecord`, `getPages()` `view` routes)
- Omitting View from resource table `recordActions`
- Visible text labels on ungrouped table record actions (icons only; Filament Tippy tooltips + a11y labels remain — see `docs/ui-tooltips.md`)
- Raw `->dateTime()` alone on `created_at` resource columns — use `since()` + `dateTimeTooltip()` instead
- Browser-native `title=` tooltips on icon CTAs — use `->tooltip()` / `x-tooltip` instead
